We are looking to sell our used MK4i swerve modules and spare parts. Here are the details. Prices are plus shipping and PayPal transaction fee. We will be at SCRIW on Oct 11th if anyone wants to pick up.

  • 5x SDS MK4i L2 used $190 per

  • 1x SDS MK4i L2 used, missing 15T bevel gear, and cancoder cover hardware $160,

  • 4x SDS L3 Gearset new $120 for all,

  • 1x SDS L2 Gearset new $30,

  • 10x SDS Billet wheel new $20 per,

  • 2x SDS Billet wheel used $20 for both,

  • 6x SDS Kit Adapter 16T Drive Pinion kraken new $100 for all,

  • 5x Vex Grip Lock Wheel V2 new w/hubs and hardware $75 for all,

  • 22x Vex Grip Lock Wheel V2 used $3 per,

  • 16x Vex Grip Lock Wheel V1 new $5 per,

  • 11x SDS Kit Pinion Gear (MK4i Kraken) new $150 for all,

  • 10x Vex Grip Lock SDS Hub w/hardware $15 for all,

  • 2x SDS Bevel Gear 45T new $40 for all,

  • 3x SDS Bevel Gear 45T used $50 for all,

  • Assorted box of SDS hardware $20

Or buy everything for $1850
